				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/Dung-%C4%90%C3%A0i/poem-bbTsS07VD0LVB5Dn1FDGYw">Dung Đài - 榕臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/author-QKy6LHJMqAcMRcgSw6RXSA">Lưu Khắc Trang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-%E1%BB%A8c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-V%C5%A9-n%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-nPkC7HAvctsY8fAfzQTEuw">Đề Vũ nương miếu - 題武娘廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-%E1%BB%A8c/author-aypZAyfagdEFp3zZZL3dzQ">Ngô Thì Ức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Bi%E1%BB%81n/Ng%C3%B4n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-6yTtwihCAN90tDOwQ7oNyw">Ngôn hoài - 言懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Bi%E1%BB%81n/author-qy2T-nw-JtHl_3EhgglyKg">Cao Biền</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/Nguy%E1%BB%87t-%C3%81ng-s%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0n-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-tYjE41zynjWuYDKo1b7VAA">Nguyệt Áng sơn hàn đường - 月盎山寒堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/author-4trx3YJ-cefKhX0g_XM7Sw">Trần Minh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Qu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-WwDsTB1mrksavELcH5wndg">Quân hành - 軍行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%C3%A1i/T%C3%A1i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-VpfVbQ1wpuh3v_4K4ByMsQ">Tái thượng khúc kỳ 2 - 塞上曲其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%C3%A1i/author-B8DdFA5Cqj7bOGn1l3xJag">Thương Thái</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%A2y-s%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-8vWpj6rNYfT0q3jhwPZ_og">Tây sơn kỳ 3 - 西山其二三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-fZekov0n38p16zJzIaCBWA">Thu dạ hoài ngâm - 秋夜懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-bi%E1%BB%87t-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-dW12UVYh-vPxg4IlKpEmEA">Tích biệt hành, tống Lưu bộc xạ phán quan - 惜別行送劉僕射判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-T%C3%B4-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Th%C3%A0nh/poem-ntePeM4NDdtMaNEF9Lu2SA">Vịnh Tô Hiến Thành - 詠蘇憲成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
